    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_4_2571-2590",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2571-2590",
      "markText": "周密谋划，慎重行动，计划明确，谋略深远",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2571&rangeEnd=2590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2571&rangeEnd=2590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_5_12384-12458",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "12384-12458",
      "markText": "孙子有言：此兵家之胜，不可先传也。 曹操注曰：传，犹泄也。兵无常势，水无常形，临敌变化，不可先传也。故料敌在心，察机在目也。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12384&rangeEnd=12458",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12384&rangeEnd=12458"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_3_772-819",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "772-819",
      "markText": "历代注解《孙子兵法》者甚众，以曹操等十一家注最著名，而且曹操是历史上注解《孙子兵法》的第一人。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=772&rangeEnd=819",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=772&rangeEnd=819"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_3_1722-1774",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1722-1774",
      "markText": "他主张“兵以义动”的战争观，强调师出有名，符合道义。在战略战术上灵活多变，因事设奇、任势制胜，兵不厌诈。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1722&rangeEnd=1774",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1722&rangeEnd=1774"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_5_10383-10416",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10383-10416",
      "markText": "孙子有言：亲而离之。 曹操注曰：以间离之。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10383&rangeEnd=10416",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10383&rangeEnd=10416"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_5_6411-6453",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6411-6453",
      "markText": "孙子有言：吾以此知胜负矣。 曹操注曰：以七事计之，知胜负矣。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6411&rangeEnd=6453",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6411&rangeEnd=6453"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_5_531-557",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "531-557",
      "markText": "以敌我之五事较优劣，定胜负。胜负既定，然后兴师动众。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=531&rangeEnd=557",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=531&rangeEnd=557"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_6_541-593",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "541-593",
      "markText": "兴师用兵，费用庞大。野战之要，宜速不宜久。久战，则财匮；就地补给，可节省己财。知兵之将帅，关乎民命国运。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=541&rangeEnd=593",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=541&rangeEnd=593"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_16_5551-5611",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "5551-5611",
      "markText": "主不可以怒而兴师，将不可以愠而致战a。合于利而动，不合于利而止。怒可以复喜，愠可以复悦，亡国不可以复存，死者不可以复生。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5551&rangeEnd=5611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5551&rangeEnd=5611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_9_2952-3050",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2952-3050",
      "markText": "徐晃迅速占领河西为营，并修筑堑栏，以此为营垒徐晃击败夜间来偷袭的关西大将梁兴，站稳脚跟。此后，曹操率大军北渡黄河，北上蒲坂津，在徐晃的接应下再次西渡黄河，使得马超等关西军兵固守的潼关天险成为虚设。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2952&rangeEnd=3050",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2952&rangeEnd=3050"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_4_585-650",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "585-650",
      "markText": "孙子者，齐人也，名武，为吴王阖闾作兵法一十三篇j，试之妇人，卒以为将k，西破强楚入郢l，北威齐、晋。后百岁馀有孙膑m，是武之后也。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=585&rangeEnd=650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=585&rangeEnd=650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_5_430-455",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "430-455",
      "markText": "曹操曰：计者，选将、量敌、度地、料卒，计于庙堂也。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=430&rangeEnd=455",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=430&rangeEnd=455"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_8_2944-2998",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2944-2998",
      "markText": "孙子有言：守则不足，攻则有余。 曹操注曰：吾所以守者，力不足也；所以攻者，力有余也。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2944&rangeEnd=2998",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2944&rangeEnd=2998"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_12_5924-5961",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "5924-5961",
      "markText": "故用兵之法，无恃其不来a，恃吾有以待也b；无恃其不攻，恃吾有所不可攻也c。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5924&rangeEnd=5961",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5924&rangeEnd=5961"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_5_5939-5977",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5939-5977",
      "markText": "孙子有言：法令孰行？ 曹操注曰：设而不犯，犯而必诛。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5939&rangeEnd=5977",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5939&rangeEnd=5977"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_6_10952-10965",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10952-10965",
      "markText": "用兵作战贵在速胜，不宜持久",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10952&rangeEnd=10965",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10952&rangeEnd=10965"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_6_1637-1687",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1637-1687",
      "markText": "或许我们认为这有作秀或表演的成分，但不要忘了即便是有戏份在，曹操的赠赏之举，也是唯其难能，所以可贵。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1637&rangeEnd=1687",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1637&rangeEnd=1687"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_11_1983-2007",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1983-2007",
      "markText": "因此，军队抢夺制胜因素是有其利的，也是有其危的。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35034845&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1983&rangeEnd=2007",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4a732400721696dd4a7481b?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1983&rangeEnd=2007"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35034845_5_1553-1610",
